main event: An object was observed for approximately 20 minutes near Wilbur, Washington, appearing round or spherical, stationary with slight wobbling, and of white or silver color.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be at an altitude of approximately 3,000 feet., The observation was terminated when the object disappeared from view., No sound or trail was observed during the sighting., The sighting was related to Project Blue Book., An oral report was made by a citizen on July 30, 1964.
